{"tid":2007240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［參選新形勢］今時今日要立法會唔再係議政，係一侓要講「揪得」「打得」！！","createTime":"2020-05-08T08:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T08:44:43.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b60f2e8e431c0ec7746a27989b54861400e8f8b","tid":2007240,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"今時今日立法會就係講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個夾硬嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個揪得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰個就係贏家！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日做返當年黃毓民掟杯已經不能夠足以應付今日形勢<br />\n<br />\n更何況去到今日反對派都只係識舉牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲好記得當日陳偉業：「黃毓民竟然掟硬野！？我平時掟開都係軟既！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要參選嘅朋友真係要搞清楚今日形勢，<br />\n<br />\n仲話要繼續議政式抗爭根本已經嘥氣！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2252e59d88e092c4615805ea4841f96d07fc9a","tid":2007240,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5fa4fad9a9577c2e00ee85f950ec832aa0102e","tid":2007240,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ba49f4c307c8024ac98ba428395a8c63045f098","tid":2007240,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfb40f797a5c247c3965eb5bc8afed4da7fd061","tid":2007240,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:44:43.000Z